# Project Configuration Guide

This project uses several configuration files to define its behavior:

## Next.js Configuration
- [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts) - Configures Next.js features, including:
  - Image optimization settings
  - HTTP headers
  - Webpack optimization
  - Production optimizations

## TypeScript Configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration with path aliases
  - The `@/*` path alias maps to `./src/*`

## Package Dependencies
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Defines project dependencies:
  - React 19
  - Next.js 15
  - Framer Motion for animations
  - React Intersection Observer for scroll detection
  - TailwindCSS for styling

## CSS Configuration
- [postcss.config.mjs](mdc:postcss.config.mjs) - PostCSS configuration for TailwindCSS

## Linting
- [eslint.config.mjs](mdc:eslint.config.mjs) - ESLint configuration
